high_descs: Walk forward then turn left to face the stove
Pick up the back left tea kettle from the stove
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink
Wash the tea kettle in the sink then remove it
Turn left and walk over to the round dining table past the fridge
Put the tea kettle on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the washed tea kettle on the dining table

high_descs: Go forward and turn to the left to face the stove.
Pick the tea pot up from the back, left corner.
Go right and then turn to the left to face the sink.
Put the tea pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the tea pot up again.
Go left and cross the room and turn left to face the round table.
Put the tea pot down on the table to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot on a table.

high_descs: Go to the stove in front of you.
Pick up the kettle on the back left corner of the stove.
Go forward until you reach the sink, then turn left.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn left and go straight, go between the table and the fridge, then turn left to face the table.
Put the kettle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean kettle on the table.
